sequenceDiagram
    participant U  as You
    participant L  as omx (Leader)
    participant S  as .omx/state/team/
    participant W0 as Worker 0 (tmux pane)
    participant W1 as Worker 1 (tmux pane)
    participant W2 as Worker 2 (tmux pane)

    U->>L: $team 3:executor "implement feature"

    L->>S: write config.json + manifest.json + task queue
    L->>W0: tmux split-window → launch Codex (executor role)
    L->>W1: tmux split-window → launch Codex (executor role)
    L->>W2: tmux split-window → launch Codex (executor role)

    L->>S: write inbox.md for each worker (task assignment)

    W0->>S: read inbox.md → pick task-001
    W1->>S: read inbox.md → pick task-002
    W2->>S: read inbox.md → pick task-003

    loop Poll progress every N seconds
        L->>W0: tmux capture-pane → read output
        L->>W1: tmux capture-pane → read output
        L->>W2: tmux capture-pane → read output
        W0->>S: write progress.json (task-001 done)
        L->>S: read progress → rebalance → assign task-004 to W0
    end

    W0->>S: all tasks done
    W1->>S: all tasks done
    W2->>S: all tasks done

    L->>U: team complete → shutdown panes
